snippet.title: Sky News Breakfast: New COVID variant, PM writes to Macron over Channel deaths
snippet.description:
On Sky News Breakfast, we have the latest on the new coronavirus variant discovered in South Africa and Boris Johnson writes to French President Emmanuel Macron after 27 people died trying to cross the Channel.
